1
00:00:07,560 --> 00:00:08,440
Commanding General

2
00:00:08,440 --> 00:00:10,080
You disregard military intelligence today

3
00:00:10,080 --> 00:00:11,320
and you will regret it.

4
00:00:11,920 --> 00:00:13,920
How can the ravings of a madman be trusted?

5
00:00:14,040 --> 00:00:15,920
Keep playing music! Keep dancing!

6
00:00:32,840 --> 00:00:34,360
Where is this place?

7
00:00:35,760 --> 00:00:38,320
This is the Taixu Immortal Realm.

8
00:00:38,320 --> 00:00:42,240
They call me Lady Shiji.

9
00:00:43,320 --> 00:00:44,920
You are a figure from mythology.

10
00:00:45,880 --> 00:00:49,400
Your mythology is the reality here.

11
00:00:49,560 --> 00:00:50,600
How can I go back?

12
00:00:51,480 --> 00:00:53,760
You and I are bound by karma.

13
00:00:53,760 --> 00:00:56,160
I have come to help you.

14
00:00:56,160 --> 00:00:56,960
That's great!

15
00:00:56,960 --> 00:00:58,280
Then let's leave right now.

16
00:00:58,280 --> 00:00:59,600
I just disappeared like that...

17
00:00:59,600 --> 00:01:00,960
Mom and Dad must be worried sick.

18
00:01:00,960 --> 00:01:02,120
Do not rush.

19
00:01:02,120 --> 00:01:04,680
You must undergo a trial first.

20
00:01:04,680 --> 00:01:05,960
Remember this.

21
00:01:05,960 --> 00:01:07,760
Nine-River Dragon Pivot.

22
00:01:07,760 --> 00:01:09,400
Stop when you meet the dragon.

23
00:01:09,400 --> 00:01:11,160
Eye of Guixu.

24
00:01:11,160 --> 00:01:12,880
Return when you see the Ruins.

25
00:01:12,880 --> 00:01:14,520
If you wish to return,

26
00:01:14,520 --> 00:01:15,920
you must first find an object.

27
00:01:15,920 --> 00:01:17,520
This object is called

28
00:01:17,520 --> 00:01:19,480
the Water-Avoiding Pearl.

29
00:01:22,640 --> 00:01:23,560
Master.

30
00:01:23,560 --> 00:01:24,560
Your son-in-law is here.

31
00:01:24,560 --> 00:01:26,440
He says it is an urgent matter

32
00:01:26,440 --> 00:01:28,200
and seeks your counsel.

33
00:01:28,800 --> 00:01:31,560
Your nephew Li Jing pays respects to Lord Yin.

34
00:01:33,880 --> 00:01:35,040
What is this urgent matter?

35
00:01:35,040 --> 00:01:36,360
Pray, tell me.

36
00:01:37,000 --> 00:01:38,520
I have received intelligence.

37
00:01:38,520 --> 00:01:40,120
The Sea Clan is gathering a great army

38
00:01:40,120 --> 00:01:41,440
and is about to attack Chentang Pass.

39
00:01:44,560 --> 00:01:46,080
Is this true?

40
00:01:46,080 --> 00:01:46,960
Absolutely true.

41
00:01:47,480 --> 00:01:48,440
Furthermore,

42
00:01:48,440 --> 00:01:51,040
the Sea Clan is searching for clues to the Nine-River Dragon Pivot.

43
00:01:51,360 --> 00:01:53,720
This object may determine the fate of Chentang.

44
00:01:54,000 --> 00:01:56,000
Yet I do not know the details.

45
00:01:56,640 --> 00:01:58,760
Nine-River Dragon Pivot...

46
00:01:58,760 --> 00:01:59,840
For such a grave matter,

47
00:02:00,040 --> 00:02:01,360
why not report it to the Commanding General?

48
00:02:01,920 --> 00:02:04,440
The Commanding General is lost in debauchery

49
00:02:04,440 --> 00:02:05,280
and refuses to govern.

50
00:02:05,680 --> 00:02:06,680
Alas.

51
00:02:07,320 --> 00:02:09,680
You need not worry too much, nephew.

52
00:02:09,680 --> 00:02:13,680
Chentang Pass is protected by the Big Dipper Wave-Calming Array.

53
00:02:13,680 --> 00:02:14,120
Dad.

54
00:02:15,720 --> 00:02:16,640
Why are you here?

55
00:02:17,320 --> 00:02:18,760
Dad, do you know of the Water-Avoiding Pearl?

56
00:02:18,760 --> 00:02:20,360
And the Nine-River Dragon Pivot?

57
00:02:38,320 --> 00:02:41,920
This was bestowed by the Yellow Emperor.

58
00:02:41,920 --> 00:02:45,000
The Qiankun Bow and Sky-Shaking Arrow

59
00:02:45,000 --> 00:02:47,000
are the treasures guarding the Pass.

60
00:02:47,600 --> 00:02:48,200
Master.

61
00:02:48,840 --> 00:02:49,600
Sorry to disturb you.

62
00:02:49,680 --> 00:02:53,320
Are you here to pray for blessings or repay a vow?

63
00:02:53,760 --> 00:02:54,400
Neither.

64
00:02:54,800 --> 00:02:56,880
I wish to ask you about something.

65
00:02:57,760 --> 00:02:59,320
Please speak freely.

66
00:02:59,840 --> 00:03:01,360
I wonder if you have heard of

67
00:03:01,560 --> 00:03:02,520
the Nine-River Dragon Pivot?

68
00:03:04,000 --> 00:03:05,680
Nine-River Dragon Pivot...

69
00:03:06,400 --> 00:03:07,840
If you pray with sincerity,

70
00:03:08,240 --> 00:03:09,480
the Human Ancestor may guide you.

71
00:03:43,120 --> 00:03:44,720
Praise the Dragon God.

72
00:03:45,080 --> 00:03:47,640
Your believers shall offer you

73
00:03:47,640 --> 00:03:49,680
the purest sacrifice.

74
00:03:49,680 --> 00:03:52,200
Praise the Dragon God.

75
00:03:59,240 --> 00:04:01,320
Praise the Dragon God.

76
00:04:01,840 --> 00:04:03,000
Someone is coming!

77
00:04:04,400 --> 00:04:05,440
Get them!

78
00:04:05,440 --> 00:04:06,600
Catch her!

79
00:04:13,800 --> 00:04:14,880
Where do you think you're going?

80
00:04:28,400 --> 00:04:29,560
Audacious Li Jing

81
00:04:30,000 --> 00:04:32,160
How dare you interfere with the Dragon God Grand Sacrifice

82
00:04:32,400 --> 00:04:34,120
The King has long issued a clear decree

83
00:04:34,120 --> 00:04:36,720
Our human race must not worship foreign evil gods

84
00:04:36,720 --> 00:04:39,120
Does the Commanding General intend to defy the decree

85
00:04:39,800 --> 00:04:41,000
Cease your nonsense

86
00:04:41,320 --> 00:04:42,160
What evil god

87
00:04:51,920 --> 00:04:52,560
Hyah

88
00:04:52,920 --> 00:04:53,560
Hyah

89
00:04:54,760 --> 00:04:55,480
My Lord

90
00:04:55,480 --> 00:04:56,840
It is the House of Yin's people

91
00:04:57,440 --> 00:04:58,720
Let them go

92
00:05:07,040 --> 00:05:07,760
My Lord

93
00:05:07,760 --> 00:05:09,240
This place has been exposed

94
00:05:13,400 --> 00:05:14,640
Dismantle the idol

95
00:05:14,920 --> 00:05:16,680
Restart the underground palace altar

96
00:05:18,360 --> 00:05:19,160
Yes

97
00:05:28,760 --> 00:05:29,840
What is this

98
00:05:34,000 --> 00:05:36,720
This is a young dragon's molted scale

99
00:05:37,880 --> 00:05:38,920
There is writing inside

100
00:05:39,440 --> 00:05:40,160
What is written

101
00:05:40,160 --> 00:05:40,720
Let me see

102
00:05:44,240 --> 00:05:45,440
Eye of Guixu

103
00:05:45,640 --> 00:05:46,840
Nine-River Dragon Pivot

104
00:05:47,840 --> 00:05:49,160
If one wishes to go to Guixu

105
00:05:49,880 --> 00:05:50,920
one needs water-avoiding ability

106
00:05:51,520 --> 00:05:52,800
I remember now

107
00:05:54,120 --> 00:05:54,920
Legend has it

108
00:05:54,920 --> 00:05:58,600
deep in Chenjiao Tan lie the remains of an ancient flood dragon

109
00:05:59,080 --> 00:06:00,440
This ancient flood dragon's inner core

110
00:06:00,440 --> 00:06:02,520
is a natural water-avoiding treasure

111
00:06:03,080 --> 00:06:04,080
Where is Chenjiao Tan

112
00:06:04,960 --> 00:06:06,480
Two hundred li to the north

113
00:06:06,960 --> 00:06:08,360
The Kingdom of Zhongbei
